                        <h3 class="section-heading">Visual Design</h3>
                        <p>Visual design is an important part of the design process. It adds emotions to the design. So, I
                          decided a palette and a font(Open Sans) to make the screens look clean and elegant in order to
                          reduce distractions and improve usability.<br><br>
                          <img id="test" class="img-responsive" src="img/brokerx/color.jpeg" alt=""/><br><br>
                          <img id="test" class="img-responsive" src="img/brokerx/font.jpeg" alt=""/><br>
